Stage 2 of 8: Gear Up and Learn to Fight, levels 1 to 5

Erga's newbie store (from the Center of Town: four west, one south)
hands out free equipment fit for anyone under level 5; the donation
room (five north, one east) has castoffs from veterans. Wear and wield
everything, then practice on the newbie farm.

Death carries no penalty at level 5 and under, so take risks now and
learn kill, assess, and wimpy. Ask questions freely on the newbie
channel; everyone started here.

